{"tid":1558372,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[代出］其實無論係輸係贏 有樣必定要長期做","createTime":"2019-09-10T12:22:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T12:25:43.000Z","uid":278212,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7b5ebd67adbbb3bb197eb97e88eba2b8acfc9adf","tid":1558372,"uid":278212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T12:22:42.000Z","msg":"其實無論係輸係贏 有樣必定要長期做<br />\n<br />\n而家可能大家無咩方向 覺得好亂 或者有人帶風向話似雨革就輸 其實我地贏緊呀 知唔知贏緊咩 係攬炒<br />\n<br />\n我地既攬炒唔單只剩係叫國際制裁大陸<br />\n<br />\n仲有樣好好好重要既野 其實一直發生緊<br />\n就係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">長期好少人消費啦</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n不過我地終極目標唔係要搞死香港所有商人 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地係要<br />\n1. 黃色企業能夠佔市場既一席位<br />\n2. 踢走藍屍及紅色企業返大陸 令到佢地無錢<br />\n<br />\n咁先真真正正可以幫到香港 還我們一個寧靜香港<br />\n<br />\n踢走藍屍及紅色企業除左令香港變返真正香港之外<br />\n仲有：<br />\n物價下跌<br />\n鋪租比<br />\n如果之後仲未有普選既話 各行各業既功能組別都有機會有黃取得<br />\n<br />\n所以大家係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">空閒時間要多宣傳</span></strong></span>多消費黃企<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果大陸放人落黎 我地就向佢地宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁就無大陸人再放落黎"},{"pid":"dff5f27ea2d2d59d436e1c1d9cda348da235b89b","tid":1558372,"uid":278212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T12:23:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f0b5417ab219acf5fcfa68bd418639ccc95fa56","tid":1558372,"uid":278212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T12:23:36.000Z","msg":"推推推1"},{"pid":"ef23b06be8f26f168358cd86050da1cc375f70ba","tid":1558372,"uid":278212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T12:23:53.000Z","msg":"推推推2"},{"pid":"0892a6e2d558133fd0e586d60efaa990941afcb4","tid":1558372,"uid":278212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T12:24:21.000Z","msg":"推推推3"},{"pid":"66b3404f44d3cd1205eba442c3560d10837fc174","tid":1558372,"uid":278212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T12:24:38.000Z","msg":"推推推4"},{"pid":"23ed34831b9609d319650849b811a27acdd60585","tid":1558372,"uid":278212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T12:24:51.000Z","msg":"推推推5"},{"pid":"9014469cf3323d822884004c2a987d697c87110b","tid":1558372,"uid":278212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T12:25:06.000Z","msg":"推推推6"},{"pid":"44f044a1f04a269d4c7b6e9dbad4ac6ded978131","tid":1558372,"uid":278212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T12:25:30.000Z","msg":"推推推7"},{"pid":"24ecb6109739a932216bc77ca8e7f799acb5870c","tid":1558372,"uid":278212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T12:25:43.000Z","msg":"推推推8"}]}